ay 1 is dropped from mobs and to be collected.. very few items in tailoring can be storebought and it a phenomenal Time-Sink to even get to 200 not to mention above  to 250..<br>and the invested plat of  your skill is  unmentionable in terms of pp....  tens of thousands of Plat easy ,  50k+ is not an off estimate or more for than matter.<br>Hrmm so  if you  dont want to  spent the 50-80k+ to master the trade and the 6 months of pure  time spent on mastering it each and everyday  then  dont bitch and complain  about &quot;over pricing&quot; this price is more than fair for the level of difficulty of making/ aquiring the items and actually fashioning the robe.<br>Not only that  but this robe is very rare and rarely ever made since  the lv of difficuly of it,  and the sheer numbers in losses is  absurd.. this is the hardest of all Velious armors to fashion and IMHO not worth  the time becuse  trying to find the people to kill the Burrowers is  extremlly hard<br><br>Oh and people like you with your undercutting are only hurting  the Tradeskills as a whole,  until the price goes so low that the items arent worth making anymore  WTG you  inconsiderate newb !<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
